Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.93,0:24:30.52,Meshi_EDCN2,,66,0,22,,{\an7\frz-90\fn@FZYaSong-B-GBK}振作一些吧 摇晃的双腿用上全力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.94,0:24:34.61,Meshi_EDCN2,,66,0,22,,{\an7\frz-90\fn@FZYaSong-B-GBK}嘴里哼着以往的风向标
